---
description: Freeze screen visuals during cleanup
globs: ["app/**/*.{ts,tsx}", "src/**/*.{ts,tsx}", "components/**/*.{ts,tsx}", "pages/**/*.{ts,tsx}"]
alwaysApply: true
---

For existing rendered screens and reusable UI components, treat the visual result as frozen.

Strictly forbidden unless explicitly requested:
- changing visible structure
- changing wrappers around visible elements
- changing spacing or dimensions
- changing text styling
- changing icon position or scale
- changing animation feel, timing, easing, or duration
- changing overlay appearance
- changing modal appearance
- changing chat, feed, wallet, live, inbox, profile, membership, or create screen appearance

Allowed:
- fix broken logic
- fix typing
- fix imports
- fix event handlers
- improve performance
- remove dead code only if rendered result stays identical

Default behavior:
screen visuals are locked.
